CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 11, 1961, p. 2, reads: "Candidates Work Hard in Victory Quest - Incumbent Constable - Incumbent Fifth Ward Democratic Constable Thomas J. (Tommy) Smith, confers with Third District Committeewoman Adreana Allen and her friend, Matthew Anderson, at Ammon Center, Tuesday.  Smith won. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Matthew Allen, Adreana Allen, and Thomas J. "Tommy" Smith, standing in front of Ammon Center
